				<p>Yummity yum.</p>
<p>First, I’ve already ordered the cookbook.</p>
<p>Second, I’ve got one of these chilling in the fridge right now.  It
looks just wonderful.  I have some thoughts, though.  I only have 9-inch
 cake pans, so I ran with them, and it is still a sky-high cake. Also, I
 thought some of the methods were unusual.  The cake directions have you
 mix the oil and sour cream in, first.  I tried, but my
inner-anti-over-beating bell was screaming, so I ended up combining
water through beaten eggs and adding all at once, so that I could
minimize the stirring.  Cake ended up delicate and tasty. I’m not saying
